{"article_id":"YrOpHJZlACFL8BwB","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Senior advisor to President Donald Trump , Jared Kusher","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"-- who is also the president 's son-in-law --","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"has officially lost the ability","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"to review sensitive classified information","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"after failing to obtain a permanent security clearance .","depth":3},{"id":5,"text":"Speculation","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"surrounding whether Kushner 's permanent security clearance , in addition to temporary clearances","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"held by dozens of White House Staffers ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"would come through","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"has been swirling for weeks .","depth":3},{"id":10,"text":"Last week President Trump said","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"it was up to Chief of Staff John Kelly to determine whether his son-in-law would continue to review classified information .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"\" That ' ll be up to General Kelly .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"General Kelly respects Jared a lot","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"and General Kelly will make that call .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"I won ' t make that call , \"","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Trump said last week during a press conference with the Australian Prime Minister at the White House .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"Previously , Kushner had access to President Trump 's daily intelligence briefings and reports .","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"Moving forward , he will not .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"Ivanka Trump ,","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"married to Kusher ,","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"has also been working at the White House on a temporary clearance .","depth":4},{"id":22,"text":"The White House ' s handling of clearances came under scrutiny after reports","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"that Kelly had been aware","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"that former staff secretary Rob Porter ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"who was accused by his two ex-wives of verbal and physical abuse ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"did not have a full security clearance","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"in part because of a previous protective order","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"granted during one of his divorces .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"The scandal prompted Kelly to crack down on staffers","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"working","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"without full clearance ,","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"more than a year into the Trump administration .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"In a five-page document","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"released last week ,","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"Kelly ordered a series of initiatives","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"aimed at bolstering protocols .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"\" The American people deserve a White House staff","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"that meets the highest standards","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"and that has been carefully vetted","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"- especially those","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"who work closely with the president","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"or handle sensitive national security information , \"","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"Kelly said in the memo .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"\" We should","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"- and in the future , must -","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"do better . \"","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"The White House argues","depth":4},{"id":48,"text":"Kushner will continue to fulfill an important role at the White House ,","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"regardless of his access level to classified information .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":99,"left":59,"right":98,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":59,"left":54,"right":58,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":54,"left":53,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":53,"left":51,"right":52,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":51,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"